import React from 'react' import { useState } from 'react' const Addtask = () => { const[Title,setTitle]=useState('') const[Day,setDay]=useState('') const[Time,setTime]=useState('') const[Reminder,setReminder]=useState(false) return (
setTitle(e.target.value)} placeholder="Title"/>
setDay(e.target.value)} />
setTime(e.target.value)} />
setReminder(e.target.checked)} />
) } export default Addtask
